/// Data Worker - ORM Backend for JTAG System
///
/// PURPOSE: Provide high-performance ORM layer for data operations
/// Receives StorageQuery from TypeScript, translates to SQL, executes via rusqlite
///
/// Implements:
/// - ping: Health check
/// - open-database: Opens SQLite database
/// - ensure-schema: Creates table schemas
/// - create-record: Creates a record
/// - read-record: Reads a record by ID
/// - query-records: ORM query with filters, sort, cursor
/// - count-records: Efficient COUNT(*) queries

